==English==
===Etymology===
From the [[diamond]] shape of a conventional [[bicycle]] [[frame]] created by the two [[triangle]]s [[head tube]], [[top tube]], [[down tube]] and [[seat tube]] and the seat tube, [[chain stays]] and [[seat stays]].

